## Framework Categories
1. **Priority Frameworks** - RICE, MoSCoW, Value vs Effort, ICE, Kano Model
2. **Discovery Frameworks** - Jobs To Be Done, Design Thinking, Lean Canvas
3. **Strategy Frameworks** - Product Vision Board, Business Model Canvas, OKRs
4. **Metrics Frameworks** - HEART, Pirate Metrics (AARRR), North Star
5. **Development Frameworks** - Agile, Scrum, Lean Development, Shape Up
6. **Growth Frameworks** - Growth Loop, Hook Model, Product-Led Growth
